{"tid":2307802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"倚矮牆趷腳下望 驚見有人倒卧  憶述梓樂滿口血 街坊激動抽泣","createTime":"2020-12-01T11:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T11:51:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b49d4e08ebcdb0dc8b4f79106150b1de195d6c","tid":2307802,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/DTWR4I4NAJH5ZJGUUMGFER3GYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FDTWR4I4NAJH5ZJGUUMGFER3GYM%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0v3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=7ee5321c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FDTWR4I4NAJH5ZJGUUMGFER3GYM%2F&h=66cbdb7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/DTWR4I4NAJH5ZJGUUMGFER3GYM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n倚矮牆趷腳下望 驚見有人倒卧 <br />\n憶述梓樂滿口血 街坊激動抽泣<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】22歲科大男生周梓樂去年在警民衝突期間墮樓後不治，死因研訊繼續，昨傳召兩名按目前證供最先發現梓樂倒地的街坊。其中原打算在三樓察看外圍情況的青年，稱無意間向下望見倒卧二樓的梓樂滿口鮮血，嘴巴似「郁吓郁吓」，不知是否想說話。他憶述梓樂狀況時一度激動抽泣，無法說話。另一名在二樓一度走近梓樂墮下位置的人則稱，曾聽見「類似跌落嚟嘅聲音」，他以為是催淚彈墜落，聲音驅使他遠離該處。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：籲報料：微不足道資訊拼埋有用<br />\n<br />\n供稱在停車場三樓向下望到梓樂墮樓後面容的將軍澳街坊崔家朗，作供初期表現冷靜，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/66LVFHdJnlVcIlK8_m-SBNpgQms=/2175x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NPTJLPY3IFGSHNJSBAGVRZ5H24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F66LVFHdJnlVcIlK8_m-SBNpgQms%3D%2F2175x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNPTJLPY3IFGSHNJSBAGVRZ5H24.jpg&h=c0f27177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「白帽男」崔家朗昨出庭作供，指發現梓樂時他已滿口鮮血且嘴巴曾郁動，不知是否想說話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發現梓樂後即跑開找急救員<br />\n<br />\n崔指看到地面有防暴警及警車，他趷起腳打算觀察車場外行人路，但向下望時見有人倒卧，他聲音顫抖地說，當時梓樂「瞓咗喺我下面，隔籬有一灘血」。他隨即跑開求助，邊跑邊大叫謂：「我想搵人幫手，我想搵first aid（急救員）！」在三樓行車路他遇見一名穿黑色風褸的年輕男子，隨即帶他到原本身處位置，再自己跑開求助。<br />\n<br />\n崔曾跑往天橋求救，「一路嗌、一路跑」，再回到二樓確認梓樂情況，「嘗試問佢有冇事，但佢畀唔到反應我」。他憶述梓樂嘴巴「好似郁吓郁吓」，不知是想說話還是因嘴巴有血。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n崔形容，當時梓樂介乎側卧與趴地之間，面向街外，背向停車位矮牆，身旁應沒人。研訊主任問他最初觀察梓樂長達十多秒，是。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n崔指當晚沒在停車場看見警員，但從天橋進入停車場二樓半時聞到催淚煙味，「少少刺鼻」但沒影響呼吸。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陪審員問三樓泊車位有否特別，崔指他站立位置有一大灘水，「行過去一定會濕，記得灘水係彈上小腿，我覺得好污糟，所以清晰記得。」站立位置左右兩邊的車位當時沒車，灘水位亦不算高，「踩完隻腳會濕，但未至於有水花」。有陪審員問，崔與其他現場人士有否互通警察動向消息，崔稱沒仔細交流警力分佈，但進入停車場前，有人叫他小心點，稱可能有危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j7AAmKDoDkVRqnqDhUNYUMfYAwI=/2641x1397/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3LVSITSRYNBVPFCTW5MTL74AEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj7AAmKDoDkVRqnqDhUNYUMfYAwI%3D%2F2641x1397%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3LVSITSRYNBVPFCTW5MTL74AEQ.jpg&h=bc840818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■崔家朗（箭嘴示）當日由三樓跑往天橋欲找人幫忙，與消防員擦身而過。領展CCTV截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hPuvw6ornuPNF4xoZZkj1jqs55E=/1579x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I3VHQV44DBCRVEYHHNA7K2MI44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhPuvw6ornuPNF4xoZZkj1jqs55E%3D%2F1579x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI3VHQV44DBCRVEYHHNA7K2MI44.jpg&h=fec6dce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周梓樂案發當晚墮樓重傷，消防員及急救員在場施救。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一街坊聞墜地聲 以為催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n另一名看到梓樂倒地的街坊莫漢斌供稱，原在車場二樓半湊熱鬧及圍觀警察放催淚彈，有警員用電筒照入停車場，而催淚煙味道令沒戴口罩的他感到少許澀眼。他稱最初見到梓樂已墮地時，梓樂身旁沒人，幾十秒後有人走近梓樂問有沒有事，梓樂無回應，有人說梓樂「中催淚彈跌咗落嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n莫稱凌晨1時03分在梓樂墮。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：CCDI932/19<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UxE2F1B79B4cHkz34eqxq_FTVNE=/1788x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UBHTIZNDLBDA3KK5JBQLLWP2WI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUxE2F1B79B4cHkz34eqxq_FTVNE%3D%2F1788x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUBHTIZNDLBDA3KK5JBQLLWP2WI.jpg&h=ffb3735d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■街坊莫漢斌昨指在停車場聞到催淚煙味道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rmD4qWKLm6C32kjb8qjmyPtda88=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5TUZSJQ475H4ZB4PR5CQHDYOJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrmD4qWKLm6C32kjb8qjmyPtda88%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5TUZSJQ475H4ZB4PR5CQHDYOJM.jpg&h=95c45cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■防暴警在案發日凌晨1時06分曾向停車場射催淚彈。有線新聞截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4MVKd_9Ilmng5gfsvCiKr__tllo=/2115x869/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RLKQDLM6JZANDCTAM34JCEOSYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4MVKd_9Ilmng5gfsvCiKr__tllo%3D%2F2115x869%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRLKQDLM6JZANDCTAM34JCEOSYI.jpg&h=785783a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fcf83f3421e1db29661d2246129eaec6be33373","tid":2307802,"uid":58896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"毋忘梓樂<br />\n還香港人公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cf3b7dae1e6dfbdaa264045f39752e9ff8c510","tid":2307802,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c865f86031da3a99f8df8ce4ee31ba2c8bf79789","tid":2307802,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"周同學父母真係慘，聽住人地講返個仔死𠴱一刻係點"},{"pid":"93c96c735912be66a811cb549d269d7e049098ca","tid":2307802,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f9321924ac6f093ac0646ee5ed2fd51ae854221","tid":2307802,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fcf83f3421e1db29661d2246129eaec6be33373","tid":2307802,"uid":58896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"毋忘梓樂<br />\n還香港人公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577110d98f6cf716e4dc7a63fd777fd3251eb584","tid":2307802,"uid":126317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"周同學，香港人會盡力為你討個公義！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}